ass=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 z-0\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex h-full items-center justify-center text-center text-white px-4\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-4 max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-white/55\">Thoothukudi&#x27;s Trusted Event Planners</p><h2 class=\"font-display text-white text-4xl font-bold md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.15]\">Every Celebration Deserves<!-- --> <span class=\"italic\">a Perfect Stage.</span></h2><h1 class=\" font-display\"></h1><p class=\"text-sm md:text-base text-white/70 max-w-lg leading-relaxed\">Décor, pandhal, catering, stage, DJ, lighting &amp; more —<br class=\"hidden md:block\"/>GJ Event Management brings every detail to life, right here in Thoothukudi.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 mt-1\"><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/25 bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm\">Birthday Themes</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/25 bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm\">School &amp; College Events</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/25 bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm\">Weddings</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/25 bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm\">DJ &amp; Lighting</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/25 bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm\">Catering</span><span class=\"rounded-full border border-white/25 bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm\">Pandhal &amp; Stages</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-3 mt-2\"><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#4b164c] shadow-lg transition hover:bg-white/90 active:scale-95\" href=\"/Booking\">Book Your Event<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-up-right h-4 w-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7 7h10v10\"></path><path d=\"M7 17 17 7\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"tel:+919843358537\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/30 bg-white/10 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white backdrop-blur-sm transition hover:bg-white/20 active:scale-95\">+91 63805 84448</a></div><p class=\"text-xs text-white/40 mt-1\">Open 24 hours · Anna Nagar, Thoothukudi</p></div></div></section><section id=\"Reach\" aria-labelledby=\"reach-heading\" class=\"scroll-mt-24 bg-white py-20 md:py-28\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-6\"><div class=\"grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px)\"><p class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center gap-2.5 rounded-full border border-secondary/40 bg-white/70 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-secondary shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(221,136,207,0.12)] backdrop-blur-sm\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-secondary\"></span><span class=\"min-w-0 break-words\">Tamil Nadu Reach</span></p><h2 id=\"reach-heading\" class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold text-primary md:text-4xl\"><span class=\"font-serif italic\">Where we produce</span> events</h2><p class=\"mt-4 leading-relaxed text-primary/70\">Headquartered in Thoothukudi, Tamil Nadu — we are a full-service event management and decoration company, with teams deployed across South Tamil Nadu for weddings, corporate events, and cultural celebrations.</p><div class=\"mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\"><a href=\"/Contact\"><div class=\"glass rounded-2xl group flex items-center justify-between p-4 transition-colors hover:bg-light\"><div><p class=\"font-bold text-primary\">Thoothukudi</p><p class=\"text-xs text-primary/50\">Headquar