op-blur overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative h-52 w-full flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background-color:#f8e7f6\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565598469107-2bd14ae7e7e4?q=80&amp;w=2123&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;ixlib=rb-4.1.0&amp;ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D\" alt=\"Event Coordination photo\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-12 bg-gradient-to-t from-white/80 to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8 md:p-10\"><p class=\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-secondary\">Timeline, vendors, and on-day support</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-2xl font-bold text-primary md:text-3xl\">Event Coordination</h3><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-primary/65 md:text-base\">Keeps the moving parts aligned so every setup is ready on time and the celebration feels calm from start to finish.</p></div></article></div><div class=\"sticky\" style=\"top:calc(128px + 24px);z-index:41\"><article class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-white/70 bg-white/85 shadow-[0_24px_70px_rgba(75,22,76,0.12)] backdrop-blur overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative h-52 w-full flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background-color:#f8e7f6\"><img src=\"https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_photo-1677529496297-fd0174d65941?q=80&amp;w=2070&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;ixlib=rb-4.1.0&amp;ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D\" alt=\"Creative Planning photo\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-12 bg-gradient-to-t from-white/80 to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8 md:p-10\"><p class=\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-secondary\">Concepts, themes, and event styling</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-2xl font-bold text-primary md:text-3xl\">Creative Planning</h3><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-primary/65 md:text-base\">Translates your occasion into a clear decoration plan with colors, floral cues, stage styling, and guest-flow details.</p></div></article></div><div class=\"sticky\" style=\"top:calc(128px + 48px);z-index:42\"><article class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-white/70 bg-white/85 shadow-[0_24px_70px_rgba(75,22,76,0.12)] backdrop-blur overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative h-52 w-full flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background-color:#f8e7f6\"><img src=\"https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_photo-1661277666101-01fb123f2a4c?q=80&amp;w=2070&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop&amp;ixlib=rb-4.1.0&amp;ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D\" alt=\"Panthal Decoration photo\" class=\"h-full w-full object-cover\"/><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-12 bg-gradient-to-t from-white/80 to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div></div><div class=\"p-8 md:p-10\"><p class=\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-secondary\">Traditional setup and venue decoration</p><h3 class=\"mt-4 text-2xl font-bold text-primary md:text-3xl\">Panthal Decoration</h3><p class=\"mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-primary/65 md:text-base\">Creates beautiful traditional panthal arrangements with floral work, entrance designs, cultural elements, and complete venue styling.</p></div></article></div></div></div></section><section id=\"about\" aria-labelledby=\"reach-heading\" class=\"scroll-mt-24 bg-white py-20 md:py-28\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 md:px-6\"><div class=\"grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px)\"><p class=\"inline-flex max-w-full items-center gap-2.5 rounded-full border border-secondary/40 bg-white/70 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-secondary shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(221,136,207,0.12)] backdrop-blur-sm\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-secondary\"></span><span class=\"min-w-0 break-words\">Industry Depth</span></p><h2 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold text-primary md:text-4xl\"><span class=\"font-serif italic\">Who we work</span> with</h2><p class=\"mt-4 leading-relaxed text-primary/70\">Over 15 years across every major celebration type in Tamil Nadu. Each event brings its own traditions, stakeholders, and storytelling — we honour them all.</p><ul class=\"mt-8 space-y-4\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span><span class=\"font-medium text-primary\">Weddings &amp; Receptions</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span><span class=\"font-medium text-primary\">Engagements &amp; Muhurtham</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span><span class=\"font-medium text-primary\">Church Ceremony &amp; First Holy Communion</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span><span class=\"font-medium text-primary\">Corporate &amp; Business Events</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span><span class=\"font-medium text-primary\">Government &amp; Public Sector</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span><span class=\"font-medium text-primary\">Birthdays &amp; Milestones</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span><span class=\"font-medium text-primary\">Cultural Programmes</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span><span class=\"font-medium text-primary\">Exhibitions &amp; Trade Shows</span></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent\"></span><span class=\"font-medium text-primary\">Hospitality &amp; Tourism</span></li></ul></div></div></div></section><section id=\"insights\" clas